{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295150/extras/ITDW_Steam.png?t=1735449416\" /><br>Stranded and alone, you must scavenge resources, craft weapons, build shelters and fight your way through a treacherous open-world environment teeming with monsters, wildlife, forgotten temples, and derelict research facilities. <br>Beware, you are not the only one exploring this lost land, for a mysterious dragon freely roams the skies and stalks the grounds, and it is never too far away.<br><br><strong>ISLAND SURVIVAL</strong><br><br>Embark on a relentless quest for survival as you scavenge materials, hunt for food, mine resources, and build your base. Keep your wits about you as a variety of ancient predators also call the island home. Adapt, innovate, and improvise as you strive to overcome the unknown challenges that lie ahead.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295150/extras/Survie_the_Island_GIF_Small.gif?t=1735449416\" /><br><br><br><strong>CRAFT TOOLS AND WEAPONS</strong><br><br>Craft an assortment of tools, equipment and weapons to overcome the island's many obstacles. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295150/extras/Tools_Gif_Small.gif?t=1735449416\" /><br><br><br><strong>BUILD YOUR BASE</strong><br><br>Whether it's in the rainforest, swamp, beach or overlooking a vista, your base serves as a vital hub for replenishment, crafting, farming, storage, and defense. Utilize a versatile modular building system to craft your perfect sanctuary, personalizing it to suit you.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295150/extras/Builing_GIF_Small.gif?t=1735449416\" /><br><br><br><strong>BEWARE THE DRAGON</strong><br><br>Roaming the open skies and stalking the lands, a mysterious Dragon also hunts the island in real-time and will unleash devastation upon the unprepared. Stay alert and always be aware.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295150/extras/Drakken_Gif_Small.gif?t=1735449416\" /><br><br><br><strong>UNCOVER AN ANCIENT MYSTERY</strong><br><br>Discover the island's mysterious temples and ancient structures, each concealing intricate puzzles and treacherous traps. Navigate through these enigmatic challenges to unlock valuable artifacts and advance your journey through the game. From navigating winding mazes to evading deadly mechanisms, every step forward brings you closer to unraveling the island's secrets and revealing its hidden truths.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295150/extras/Temples_GIF_Small.gif?t=1735449416\" /><br><br><br><strong>EXPLORE THE ISLAND'S MANY BIOMES</strong><br><br>Venture through the diverse biomes of the island, each offering its own unique ecosystem and challenges to overcome. From lush forests teeming with life to arid deserts where survival is a constant struggle, the island's biomes provide a rich tapestry of environments to explore. Traverse snowy mountain peaks, murky swamps, and deep caves, each presenting its own set of hazards and rewards.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295150/extras/Biome_GIF_Small__2_.gif?t=1735449416\" />","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295150/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1735449416","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295150/page.bg.jpg?t=1735449416","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295150/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1735449416","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295150/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1735449416","cat